        Compares two String[] objects Arguments are first compared by existence, then by # of elements, then by values.
        Parameters:
        stringarray0 - First String[] to compare.
        stringarray1 - Second String[] to compare.
        descending - flags indicating comparison order. true = descending, false = ascending.
        Returns:
